# Different Card ï¼ˆfacebook, prob)
What is the probability of pulling a different color or shape card from a shuttled deck of 52 cards?

# Answer
P(different color or shape card) = 1 - P(pulling same color and shape card) = 1 - (12/51) = 39/51

